e8621ab-0 jwmryO sc-3ddd79c0-7 rkpEx"><a href="/users/boyd-cothran" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 jexetL">Boyd Cothran</a><span><p>is an associate professor of history in the Department of History at York University in Toronto, Canada. His books include <a href="https://uncpress.org/book/9781469676555/the-edwin-fox/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>The Edwin Fox: How an Ordinary Sailing Ship Connected the World in the Age of Globalization, 1850-1914</em></a> (2023), with co-author Adrian Shubert, <a href="https://uncpress.org/book/9781469633343/remembering-the-modoc-war/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>Remembering the Modoc War: Redemptive Violence and the Making of American Innocence</em></a> (2014) and the co-edited <a href="https://www.bloomsbury.com/uk/women-warriors-and-national-heroes-9781350121133/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>Women Warriors and National Heroes: Global Histories</em></a> (2020).</p></span></div><div class="sc-2e8621ab-0 jwmryO sc-3ddd79c0-7 rkpEx"><a href="/users/adrian-shubert" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 jexetL">Adrian Shubert</a><span><p>is professor emeritus in history at York University in Toronto, Canada. He is the author of <a href="https://uncpress.org/book/9781469676555/the-edwin-fox/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"><em>The Edwin Fox: How an Ordinary Sailing Ship Connected the World in the Age of Globalization, 1850-1914</em></a> (2023), with co-author Boyd Cothran, and <a href="https://utorontopress.com/9781487508609/the-sword-of-luchana/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>The Sword of Luchana: Baldomero Espartero and the Making of Modern Spain, 1793-1879</em></a> (2021).</p></span></div><br/><div class="sc-3ddd79c0-9 eACYrZ"><p>Edited by<a href="/users/samhaselby" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 jexetL">Sam Haselby</a></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-114c07c9-0 iNdsQY"><span>5,100<!-- --> words</span><span class="sc-114c07c9-1 bvsiTx"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="16" height="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-comment-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.303,16.553l1.107,3.783l-3.48-2.322c-0.689,0.234-1.422,0.371-2.193,0.371c-1.041,0-2.024-0.234-2.907-0.642 c2.034-1.697,3.333-4.275,3.333-7.166c0-1.994-0.625-3.836-1.677-5.347c0.406-0.073,0.823-0.117,1.251-0.117 c3.762,0,6.814,2.971,6.814,6.634c0,1.594-0.578,3.057-1.539,4.2L21.303,16.553z M15.255,10.684c0,3.861-3.213,6.99-7.176,6.99 c-0.812,0-1.583-0.144-2.31-0.391l-3.667,2.446l1.166-3.985l-0.744-0.638c-1.013-1.203-1.621-2.743-1.621-4.423 c0-3.858,3.215-6.987,7.176-6.987C12.042,3.696,15.255,6.825,15.255,10.684z"></path></svg><span>4<!-- --> <!-- -->comments</span></span><span class="sc-114c07c9-2 hRWhru"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="17" height="17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span>Save</span></span></div><br/><div class="sc-5c8686bf-1 hEDaTq"><a class="sc-45649ee9-0 fOpabg sc-5c8686bf-0 fFoFgq" href="/syndication?article_slug=how-a-single-unglamorous-ship-tells-the-history-of-the-world&amp;article_name=One%20ship,%20many%20stories&amp;author=Boyd%20Cothran,%20Adrian%20Shubert&amp;date=30%20January%202024"><span class="sc-45649ee9-1 cacrwE">Syndicate this <!-- -->essay</span></a></div><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 bSqqMf sc-3ddd79c0-13 kNGStK"><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 bSqqMf"><div><br/></div><div class="sc-81b64237-0 QBKQT"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="24" height="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-comment-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.303,16.553l1.107,3.783l-3.48-2.322c-0.689,0.234-1.422,0.371-2.193,0.371c-1.041,0-2.024-0.234-2.907-0.642 c2.034-1.697,3.333-4.275,3.333-7.166c0-1.994-0.625-3.836-1.677-5.347c0.406-0.073,0.823-0.117,1.251-0.117 c3.762,0,6.814,2.971,6.814,6.634c0,1.594-0.578,3.057-1.539,4.2L21.303,16.553z M15.255,10.684c0,3.861-3.213,6.99-7.176,6.99 c-0.812,0-1.583-0.144-2.31-0.391l-3.667,2.446l1.166-3.985l-0.744-0.638c-1.013-1.203-1.621-2.743-1.621-4.423 c0-3.858,3.215-6.987,7.176-6.987C12.042,3.696,15.255,6.825,15.255,10.684z"></path></svg> <!-- -->4<!-- --> <!-- -->Comments</div><div class="sc-531dc212-0 gowMUU"><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-email" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M22 6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6zm-2 0l-8 5-8-5h16zm0 12H4V8l8 5 8-5v10z"></path></svg><span class="sc-531dc212-2 gjonPf">Email</span></div><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-531dc212-2 gjonPf">Save</span></div><div><svg viewBox="0 0 256 209" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-twitter" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M256,25.4500259 C246.580841,29.6272672 236.458451,32.4504868 225.834156,33.7202333 C236.678503,27.2198053 245.00583,16.9269929 248.927437,4.66307685 C238.779765,10.6812633 227.539325,15.0523376 215.57599,17.408298 C205.994835,7.2006971 192.34506,0.822 177.239197,0.822 C148.232605,0.822 124.716076,24.3375931 124.716076,53.3423116 C124.716076,57.4586875 125.181462,61.4673784 126.076652,65.3112644 C82.4258385,63.1210453